				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Alternatively, you can do this after setting $2006 to #$20 and #$00 (or whatever nametable you are wanting to):
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp;ldx #$00<br />clear:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $2007<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $2007<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $2007<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $2007<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;dex<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;bne clear<br /></div>
<br />
<br />Since $2007 increments itself, you can do this. This way you can do the loop the way you want to, 256 times. I believe I learned this from blargg's tutorial programs, but I'm not 100% sure.</div>

